  "name": "Get-IntuneAssignments",
  "description": "Get-IntuneAssignments retrieves all Intune configuration profile assignments (device configurations, policies, enrollment configurations, and more) and returns PowerShell objects for easy filtering, grid viewing, and exporting. It supports multiple authentication methods (Interactive, Certificate, ClientSecret, User/System Managed Identity), group filtering, and CSV export. It also includes coverage for Cloud PC role assignments and Intune role assignments.",
